      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "農民 土地 分配",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "農民たちは大喜びです。『ついに、自分たちの時代が来た』って。",
      "emotion": "laugh",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "農民 喜び 祝い",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "工業化を急速に進めて、『社会主義建設』を始めます。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "工場 煙突 産業",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "毛沢東は『中国を世界大国にする』と宣言しました。",
      "emotion": "shock",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "portrait",
        "keyword": "毛沢東 野心",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "50年代は、割と成功するんです。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "発展 建設 繁栄",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "GDP も上昇、識字率も上昇。毛沢東の支持は最高潮。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "グラフ 上昇 成功",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "『神』に近い存在になっていきます、毛沢東は。",
      "emotion": "think",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "神 崇拝 像",
